data.description: Home of original owners. Enter on gleaming hardwood floors opening to fireside family room with skylights to bring in natural light - Separate Dining Room with hardwood floors and corner plant window - Kitchen/Breakfast area also has Hardwood Floors and opens to deck with view of level backyard. Master Bedroom has en suite bath and his & hers closets. Convenient open staircase to basement boasts an inviting entertaining space, office space, oversized laundry room and extra storage space. Spacious 2 car garage has ample storage space.
